    "en": {
      "title": "Increase in interest rates on credit cards",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Many commercial banks in Sri Lanka have increased the annual interest rate on credit cards.",
        "Banks inform that the annual interest rate for credit cards has been increased to 36 percent.",
        "The Monetary Board of the Central Bank decided on April 08 to remove the imposed limits on the interest rates offered on credit cards.",
        "Since then, the interest rates have been increased from the previous 18% to 24%, then to 30% and now again to 36%."
      ],
